abstract: A look back on our reporting of the past week's highs and lows in finance.
snippet: A look back on our reporting of the past week's highs and lows in finance.
lead_paragraph: DealBook, a well-known early riser, fell asleep before the seventh inning Thursday night, so we know how it feels to miss out on exciting developments.1 If you're the type who worries about missing the latest deal talk, take a quick look back on our reporting of the past week's highs and lows in finance.
